<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 20:04:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国参议院领袖舒默缩短亚洲之行</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-senate-leader-schumer-cutting-short-trip-to-asia/articleshow/104323628.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104323628.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默的发言人周二在回应以色列发生的事件时表示，他将缩短亚洲之行，并于周四返回美国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 17:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-senate-leader-schumer-cutting-short-trip-to-asia/articleshow/104323628.cms</guid></item><item><title>1921 年塔尔萨种族大屠杀最后一位幸存目击者去世，享年 102 岁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/last-surviving-witness-of-1921-tulsa-race-massacre-passes-away-at-102/articleshow/104323629.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104323629.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;休斯·范·埃利斯 (Hughes Van Ellis) 是 1921 年塔尔萨种族大屠杀的最后幸存者之一，现已去世，享年 102 岁。埃利斯被称为“红叔叔”，他是塔尔萨市赔偿诉讼的主要原告，寻求对塔尔萨市的赔偿责任负责。大屠杀的后果。埃利斯于 2021 年在众议院司法小组委员会作证，要求对幸存者和后代进行赔偿。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 17:48:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/last-surviving-witness-of-1921-tulsa-race-massacre-passes-away-at-102/articleshow/104323629.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争颠覆拜登双管齐下的中东战略</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/analysis-israel-hamas-war-upends-bidens-two-pronged-middle-east-strategy/articleshow/104323036.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104323036.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;近期以色列和哈马斯之间的暴力升级，让拜登政府的中东政策陷入危机。美国政府曾希望促成以色列和沙特阿拉伯之间的缓和，并遏制伊朗的核野心。然而，哈马斯的袭击使这些目标变得复杂，并对正常化努力的未来提出了疑问。它还因排挤巴勒斯坦人而受到批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:49:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/analysis-israel-hamas-war-upends-bidens-two-pronged-middle-east-strategy/articleshow/104323036.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗：赫拉特地震死亡人数超过4000人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/afghanistan-death-toll-in-herat-earthquakes-surpasses-4000/articleshow/104323135.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104323135.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据塔利班部门称，阿富汗赫拉特省发生的地震已导致 4000 多人死亡，数千座房屋被毁。灾害管理部报告称，20个村庄的1,983间住宅被毁。塔利班尚未提供死亡和受伤人数的详细信息。搜救工作正在进行中，欧盟和世界卫生组织已承诺向受害者提供援助。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 17:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/afghanistan-death-toll-in-herat-earthquakes-surpasses-4000/articleshow/104323135.cms</guid></item><item><title>关键演讲前，赫克勒在英国反对党领袖身上闪闪发光</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/heckler-showers-glitter-on-uk-opposition-leader-before-key-speech/articleshow/104323071.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104323071.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周二，当英国反对党领袖凯尔·斯塔默开始在工党年度会议上发表主题演讲时，一名质问者对他进行了攻击。斯塔默似乎并不担心，在对这一事件说了几句俏皮话后，他脱下了闪闪发光的夹克，发表了备受期待的演讲。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:53:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/heckler-showers-glitter-on-uk-opposition-leader-before-key-speech/articleshow/104323071.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯最高安全官员访问阿塞拜疆并会见总统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-top-security-official-visits-azerbaijan-meets-president/articleshow/104323464.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104323464.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯最高安全官员、俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的亲密盟友尼古拉·帕特鲁舍夫在巴库会见了阿塞拜疆总统伊利哈姆·阿利耶夫。安理会新闻处表示，双方讨论了俄罗斯与阿塞拜疆在各个领域合作的广泛问题。重点是与确保和加强区域和国际安全与稳定有关的主题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 17:38:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-top-security-official-visits-azerbaijan-meets-president/articleshow/104323464.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击后意大利的梅洛尼参观罗马犹太教堂</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-visits-rome-synagogue-after-israel-attacks/articleshow/104323049.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104323049.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊斯兰激进组织哈马斯对以色列发动袭击后，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周二在罗马一座犹太教堂拜访了犹太社区成员。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-visits-rome-synagogue-after-israel-attacks/articleshow/104323049.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙的巴勒斯坦人称以色列的轰炸感觉就像新的“灾难”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-in-gaza-say-israeli-bombardment-feels-like-new-nakba/articleshow/104322757.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104322757.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙的巴勒斯坦人表示，以色列的轰炸如此猛烈，他们感觉自己正在经历自己的“Nakba”，这是阿拉伯语中灾难的意思，指的是 1948 年以色列发动的战争，这场战争导致他们被大规模剥夺。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-in-gaza-say-israeli-bombardment-feels-like-new-nakba/articleshow/104322757.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯重返联合国人权机构的努力在投票后失败</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-bid-to-return-to-un-rights-body-fails-after-vote/articleshow/104322667.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104322667.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯周二未能重返联合国最高人权机构，其竞争对手在联合国大会上赢得了相当多的选票，这次选举被视为对西方孤立莫斯科努力的一次关键考验。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:19:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-bid-to-return-to-un-rights-body-fails-after-vote/articleshow/104322667.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧盟部长在巴勒斯坦援助分歧中举行会议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-ministers-meet-amid-divisions-over-palestinian-aid/articleshow/104322547.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104322547.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟外长召开会议讨论是否继续向巴勒斯坦人提供援助。在哈马斯最近袭击以色列后，欧盟委员会最初宣布暂停援助，但后来又收回了这一决定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:08:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-ministers-meet-amid-divisions-over-palestinian-aid/articleshow/104322547.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击造成的可怕后果：以色列发现 40 具婴儿尸体，其中一些已被肢解</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ghastly-aftermath-of-hamas-assault-bodies-of-40-babies-some-severed-found-in-israel/articleshow/104322474.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104322474.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙地带附近的卡法阿扎社区遭到哈马斯恐怖分子袭击，造成婴儿和儿童等人员伤亡。该事件被描述为以色列军官的屠杀。该地区仍然活跃，士兵们对潜在威胁保持警惕。这次袭击涉及使用枪支、手榴弹和刀具袭击平民的家中。袭击发生后，以色列军方宣布控制边境，并对加沙实施围困。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ghastly-aftermath-of-hamas-assault-bodies-of-40-babies-some-severed-found-in-israel/articleshow/104322474.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿尔维总统呼吁巴基斯坦“宽恕”并努力“加强民主”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/president-alvi-calls-for-forgiveness-efforts-to-strengthen-democracy-in-poll-bound-pakistan/articleshow/104322142.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104322142.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦总统阿里夫·阿尔维呼吁在该国即将于一月举行的大选之前结束痛苦并促进合作与宽恕。阿尔维强调了所有政党及其领导人参与选举进程以加强民主的平等机会的重要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:41:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/president-alvi-calls-for-forgiveness-efforts-to-strengthen-democracy-in-poll-bound-pakistan/articleshow/104322142.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国首相里希·苏纳克：那些支持英国哈马斯的人将被“追究责任”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/those-supporting-hamas-in-the-uk-will-be-held-to-account-pm-rishi-sunak/articleshow/104321962.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104321962.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 誓言要追究支持哈马斯的个人在最近袭击以色列后的责任。他重申对以色列的声援并谴责恐怖主义行为。苏纳克强调，哈马斯被认定为恐怖组织，并敦促人们不要支持他们。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/those-supporting-hamas-in-the-uk-will-be-held-to-account-pm-rishi-sunak/articleshow/104321962.cms</guid></item><item><title>残酷的突然袭击使以色列团结在一个目标上：粉碎哈马斯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/brutality-of-surprise-attack-unites-israel-around-one-goal-crush-hamas/articleshow/104321047.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104321047.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在造成数百名以色列人死亡的致命袭击之后，以色列正准备摧毁加沙地带的哈马斯军事基础设施。这次袭击使全国团结起来，并搁置了政治分歧。有人讨论组建紧急联合政府，但战后其可持续性仍存疑虑。有人担心冲突可能蔓延到黎巴嫩，导致真主党可能发动袭击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 14:40:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/brutality-of-surprise-attack-unites-israel-around-one-goal-crush-hamas/articleshow/104321047.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京指责美国政策失败，俄罗斯表示正在与以色列和巴勒斯坦进行对话</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-says-its-talking-to-both-israel-and-palestinians-as-putin-blames-failure-of-us-policy/articleshow/104319598.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104319598.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京周二表示，以色列和巴勒斯坦之间的暴力爆发表明美国中东政策的失败，克里姆林宫表示正在与交战双方保持联系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 13:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-says-its-talking-to-both-israel-and-palestinians-as-putin-blames-failure-of-us-policy/articleshow/104319598.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列冲突爆发后英国反犹太主义事件激增</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-antisemitic-incidents-soar-after-start-of-conflict-in-israel/articleshow/104318598.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104318598.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据犹太慈善机构社区安全信托基金 (CST) 称，英国反犹太主义事件的报道与去年同期相比增加了两倍。尽管没有提供确切的数字，但 CST 预计未来几天将会报告更多事件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 12:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-antisemitic-incidents-soar-after-start-of-conflict-in-israel/articleshow/104318598.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国人权事务高级专员谴责以色列“围困”加沙、武装分子劫持人质</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-rights-chief-condemns-israeli-siege-of-gaza-militants-taking-of-hostages/articleshow/104317662.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104317662.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国人权事务高级专员表示，以色列空袭的目标是加沙地带的住宅楼和学校。联合国还谴责巴勒斯坦武装组织的大规模杀戮和绑架人质。以色列军方已征召了30万名预备役军人，并对加沙实施全面封锁，可能是为了准备地面进攻。空袭袭击了联合国救援机构驻地，造成平民伤亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 12:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-rights-chief-condemns-israeli-siege-of-gaza-militants-taking-of-hostages/articleshow/104317662.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国检察官对哈马斯展开谋杀和绑架调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/german-prosecutor-opens-murder-and-kidnapping-probe-into-hamas/articleshow/104314958.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104314958.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国对哈马斯成员涉嫌谋杀、过失杀人和劫持人质展开调查。这项调查是在德国公民在哈马斯袭击以色列期间被绑架之后进行的。德国总理肖尔茨表示，他们正在与以色列合作，确保被绑架公民的自由和安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 11:09:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/german-prosecutor-opens-murder-and-kidnapping-probe-into-hamas/articleshow/104314958.cms</guid></item><item><title>法院驳回美国记者格什科维奇针对俄罗斯拘留的申诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/court-rejects-complaint-by-us-reporter-gershkovich-against-detention-in-russia/articleshow/104314422.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104314422.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯一家法院驳回了美国记者埃文·格什科维奇针对延长审前拘留的申诉。格什科维奇是《华尔街日报》的记者，今年三月因间谍罪被捕，但他否认了这一指控。法院的裁决意味着格什科维奇将至少被拘留到 11 月 30 日。审判日期尚未确定。格什科维奇是冷战以来首位因间谍罪在俄罗斯被拘留的美国记者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 10:54:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/court-rejects-complaint-by-us-reporter-gershkovich-against-detention-in-russia/articleshow/104314422.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国在细菌恐慌后将寻求庇护者送回驳船</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-to-return-asylum-seekers-to-barge-after-bacteria-scare/articleshow/104312218.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104312218.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国将再次将寻求庇护者安置在其南部海岸的一艘驳船上，两个月前，他们因水污染而被转移。政府希望削减安置移民的成本，但批评者称驳船不人道。这艘船是英国阻止人们从法国乘小船穿越英吉利海峡非法移民战略的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 09:51:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-to-return-asylum-seekers-to-barge-after-bacteria-scare/articleshow/104312218.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>